main.info: The aalto undergraduate centre (also known as the main building) is in the centre of Otaniemi.

alvari.info: Alvari is a student restaurant located in the undergraduate centre in the heart of Otaniemi.

Silinteri.info: Silinteri is a restaurant located in the undergraduate centre in the heart of Otaniemi.

Aino cafe.info: Aino is a cafe located in the undergraduate centre

Elissa cafe.info: Elissa is a cafe located in the U-wing in the undergraduate centre

Student services.info: Student services can be found in the undergraduate centre in the heart of Otaniemi

IT Service Desk Kandi.info: The IT service service desk can be found in the undergraduate centre

studenthub.info: The student hub is an around the clock of space for students located in the undergraduate centre

A siipi Main.info: The a wing is a wing of the main building, located on the east side. It often harbours art installations and has some computer labs equipped with 3D modeling software.

H siipi Main.info: The h wing is a wing of the main building, located on the upper floors.

K siipi Main.info: The k wing is a wing of the main building.

M siipi Main.info: The m wing is a wing of the main building.

U siipi Main.info: The u wing is a wing of the main building, located in the northern parts.

Y siipi Main.info: The y wing is a wing of the main building, located in the centre of it.

Kvarkki.info: kvarkki is a student restaurant located north of the undergraduate centre.

sodexokone.info: The student restaurant operated by Sodexo in the Mechanical Engineering building, also known as the Kone building.

kirjasto.info: The harald herlin learning center can be found south of the undergraduate center, close to the metro station.

Robert's Coffee.info: robert's coffee can be found in the harald herlin learning center

maari.info: maari is an around the clock open building harbouring many computer labs and study rooms. In this building you can also find health services for staff.

dipoli.info: Dipoli is Aalto University's main building. As a building, it represents a new type of multi-purpose design that showcases the University's expertise, activities and people. Dipoli offers the entire Aalto community and its stakeholders meeting places and work spaces as well as event and exhibition facilities.

reima.info: Reima is a student restaurant inside Dipoli. It is named after one of the architects of the building.

Otaniemen ostoskeskus.info: The otaniemi shopping center is located east of the main building. It has various shops, a grocery store, and a cafe.

Alepa Otaniemi.info: The alepa in otaniemi can be found in the shopping center.

rkioski.info: rkioski is a small kiosk in the otaniemi shopping center.

kynajapaperi.info: Kynä ja Paperi is a café located in the Otaniemi shopping center. It also serves as a school appliances shop.

otafood.info: Otafood is a chinese restaurant located in the Otaniemi shopping center.

ATM.info: There is an Otto ATM located in the otaniemi shopping center.

r020-pharmacy.info: There is a pharmacy in the Otaniemi shopping center.

T.info: The departmentent of computer science, also know as T-talo or T-house, can be found in the west region of Otaniemi.

Paniikki.info: The panique computer lab is the computer science departments own computer lab.

subway_cs.info: There exists a subway restaurant in the computer science department. It also has student prices for daily subs.
